name: Kick-List.com
overview:
Kick-list.com is a social application that allows users to collaboratively build lists of their favorite things - from books to bars - using their social networks.

Anyone can see your lists on kick-list.com, but only friends in your chosen social networks (currently Facebook with Twitter, LinkedIn, MeetUp.com and Google coming soon) can add, comment or kick things up your list. Whether sharing restaurant recommendations with Facebook friends, building a brand using Twitter followers or asking for professional advice from LinkedIn colleagues, Kick-list.com is enabling the next generation of online social interaction.
